"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-25-andy-murray-pulls-olympic-tennis-singles-retirement-drama-21294230\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Andy Murrayhas pulled out of the Olympic singles tennis tournament at the 2024ParisGames, the last event he is due to play before his retirement.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old is still competing in the men's doubles alongsideDan Evansas he fights for his fourth overall Olympic medal on the Roland-Garros clay courts.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray, though, regarded as one of Great Britain's biggest sporting heroes, will now never play a singles match ever again, bringing his superb career to an end.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 306, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5966313032301706e-13, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The legendary former world No.1 won twoWimbledontitles, two Olympic gold medals, theUSOpen and the Davis Cup - but now officially hangs up his racket.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have take the decision to withdraw from the singles to concentrate on the doubles with Dan,' Murray said on Thursday.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Our practice has been great and we are playing well together.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Really looking forward to getting started and representing GB one more time.'\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9949567402062328, \"rank\": 0.005068702163092488, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray, who ended Great Britain's 77-year wait for a champion in the Wimbledon men's singles in 2013, struggled badly with injuries in his twilight years but made an incredible comeback with a metal hip as he went on to land even more titles.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5966313032301706e-13, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He picked up a nasty back problem at Queen's Club in June - which required surgery andforced him outof one last appearance in the Wimbledon singles - although he did get anemotional farewellplaying doubles with his brother Jamie.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray registered a total of 46 ATP Tour career titles in singles, which puts him 15th overall in the Open Era.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heenjoyed 41 weeks as the world No.1- a sensational feat given the era of tennis he was playing in withNovak Djokovic, Rafael Nadal and Roger Federer.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999943777087337, \"rank\": 5.6223228868437996e-06, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1592, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murrayguided Britain to glory in the Davis Cuptoo, ending the country's 79-year wait to lift the trophy, with 2015 marking the team's first triumph since 1936.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1638, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9994750460581615, \"rank\": 0.0005251588377915986, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray, who also won Olympic Silver alongside Laura Robson in mixed doubles and was a finalist at the other two Grand Slams he did not win - Roland-Garros and the Australian Open - has struggled with various injury problems since 2016and it looked like his career was overbefore he successfully returned with a metal hip.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Robson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\"}, {\"begin\": 1927, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9169557450399954e-14, \"text\": \"Roland-Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After making a comeback, Murray worked his way back into the world top 50, won the European Open, reached three more ATP Tour finals, won the Queen's Club doubles title and lifted three trophies on the lower-level ATP Challenger Tour.\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2323, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Challenger_Tour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1329885797145814e-26, \"text\": \"ATP Challenger Tour\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Challenger_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Challenger_Tour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray confirmed in July 2023 that he was starting to think about retirement and in February this year,he announced that 2024 was 'likely'going to be his final summer in tennis, with the Olympics in Paris to beone of his last events.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2544, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999758984, \"rank\": 2.4007874454467246e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In March,Murray suffered an ankle injury,admitting that he would be ruled out for an 'extended period', but returned in time for a last dance at the French Open.\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was set to play Wimbledon singles before his back injury at Queen's Club - and after being unable to play in the Olympic singles - he's now officially retired.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Arrived in Paris for my last ever tennis tournament@OlympicsCompeting for \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ac\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00a7 have been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m extremely proud to get do it one final time!pic.twitter.com/keqnpvSEE1  Speaking before he pulled out of the Olympic singles, Murray confirmed that Paris 2024 would behis 'last tennis tournament'before retirement.\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2918, \"end\": 2923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999758984, \"rank\": 2.4007874454467246e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3181, \"end\": 3187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3203, \"end\": 3213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.123439184354414e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray posted on X: 'Arrived in Paris for my last ever tennis tournament @Olympics competing for [Great Britain].\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3270, \"end\": 3276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3302, \"end\": 3307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999758984, \"rank\": 2.4007874454467246e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3368, \"end\": 3381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5966313032301706e-13, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[It has] been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I am extremely proud to get do it one final time!'\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At Wimbledon 2024, Murraywas left in tearsas he spoke about his career on Centre Court after playing what is highly likely to be his last-ever match there.\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3573, \"end\": 3585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Centre Court\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is hard, because I would love to keep playing but I can not,' Murray said about his upcoming retirement.\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3722, \"end\": 3728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Physically it's just too tough now.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of the injuries have added up and like I said they have not been insignificant.\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want to play forever.\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love this sport.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's given me so much, taught me loads of lessons over the years that I can use for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 4035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to stop so it is hard.'\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In hispost-match press conference, Murray possibly left the door open to continuing in doubles, only specifically ruling out singles when asked if he could be tempted to make a U-turn to play Wimbledon one last time next year in 2025.\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4110, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 4267, \"end\": 4276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"score\": 0.5666270648582759, \"rank\": 0.671555138725083, \"text\": \"Wimbledon\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Wimbledon_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of all the memories Andy Murray has given us, one stands above the rest.On 7 July 2013, in living rooms and town squares across the country, we celebrated the end of a 77-year-wait\\u2026pic.twitter.com/j23kLcwkRE  'Before what happened in Miami (a nasty ankle injury) I was starting to play good tennis,' Murray added.\", \"from\": 4311, \"to\": 4624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4331, \"end\": 4342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.377474609990804e-72, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 4545, \"end\": 4550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\", \"score\": 0.9767006186997426, \"rank\": 0.023821405941893827, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\"}, {\"begin\": 4611, \"end\": 4617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6117476572196274e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'At Queens I got through the first round.\", \"from\": 4626, \"to\": 4667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can still win matches at this level.\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even with the physical issues around the hip, I was still able to compete at the highest level.\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Not as consistently as I would have liked.\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 4847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Certainly not having the results I would have wanted.\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But yeah, I can definitely still win matches here or on the grass once I am recovered from the back injury.\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 5009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do not want to do that now.\", \"from\": 5010, \"to\": 5043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I could do it, but I have no plans to play singles again.'\", \"from\": 5044, \"to\": 5109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is the full schedule for the Olympic tennis tournament, which is being played on the Paris clay, usually home to the iconic French Open.\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5201, \"end\": 5206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999758984, \"rank\": 2.4007874454467246e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star claims Andy Murray has 'unfair advantage' at Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:Why is not Emma Raducanu playing at the Olympics Games in Paris?\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5284, \"end\": 5295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.377474609990804e-72, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 5359, \"end\": 5372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res